I haven’t seen anyone mention this (sorry if I missed it in the thousand comments) but the cologne ad is 100% a Tarantino reference. He also has a brother, Vic, who is a character in Reservoir Dogs, hence the Vega Bros. Definitely a fun little criminal underworld Easter egg.
